bilingual.source: Brighton is located on the south coast of England.
bilingual.target: 布莱顿位于英格兰南海岸。

bilingual.source: The Longji Rice Terraces are located in Longsheng County.
Most of them are located in Riyadh but each gallery has a specific role.
bilingual.target: 它们大多数位于利雅得，但每个画廊都有特定的角色。

bilingual.source: Located off the coast of Australia, the Great Barrier Reef is the biggest structure made by living organisms.
bilingual.target: 大堡礁位于澳大利亚海岸，是由生物体构成的最大结构。

bilingual.source: The abbey is located on a hill.
The school is located near the river.
The testes are located in the scrotum.

yingyinNormal.en: Hong Kong is located on the southern coast of The People's Republic of China.
yingyinNormal.zh: 香港位于中华人民共和国的南岸。
机器找到萨姆恩了，扣紧安全带。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm just blown away I located your thumb.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没想到在这么偏远的地方，我还可以找到你的拇指。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Reese, have we located our old friend?
yingyinNormal.zh: 里瑟先生，找到我们的老朋友了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I've already located a suitable planet on which to establish a Vulcan colony.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已找到一个可以重建维肯星的星球了。

yingyinNormal.en: The answer is in your head. I don't have the slightest idea where the Machine's located.
yingyinNormal.zh: 答案就在你的脑袋里。我根本就不知道机器的位置。

yingyinNormal.en: And the only way to download the ledger is through the central computer terminal located there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 下载这个账册的唯一方法就是通过那地方的中央计算机终端。

yingyinNormal.en: Open Ocean! I know where that is. That's the exhibit located right next to... I don't care. Easy!
yingyinNormal.zh: 大洋区！我知道它在哪里。那个展览馆旁边就是 ... 我才不在乎。别激动！

yingyinNormal.en: Well, thank you. Pompeii was an ancient village in Italy located near the beauty and culture of Naples.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢你，庞贝是意大利的一座古城，座落于风光秀丽文化绚烂的那不勒斯附近。

yingyinNormal.en: Also, Halliday archived every film, game, book, and television program he ever saw, located on the mezzanine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时，哈利迪保存了他看过的每部电影，游戏，书籍和电视节目都存档在夹层楼底。

yingyinNormal.en: This seat is ideally located both in relation to the heat source in the winter and a cross breeze in the summer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个位置正好，能在冬天吹到暖气，夏天吹到对流风。

yingyinNormal.en: The first bathroom break isn't until the Denny's located near Bakersfield which is approximately two and half hours away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一个上厕所时间是在贝克斯菲尔德的丹尼餐厅，距此大约2个半小时。

yingyinNormal.en: It's located at one end of a 34-kilometre bridge, on an island in the open sea which was razed to build a freshwater port.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一座34公里长的桥连接着这个城市，其所在地曾是远海上一座岛 后被人类夷平了来建淡水港。

yingyinNormal.en: Your crew requires oxygen to survive, mine does not. I will target your life support systems located behind the aft nacelle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的船员需要氧气，而我的不需要。我只要攻击你们的生命保障系统它就在飞船驾驶室后面。

yingyinNormal.en: I suppose you could say they're invisible, hidden in a dark room that's at the center of a maze that's located somewhere up here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 应该说它是看不见的，就藏在迷宫中央的小黑屋里而这个迷宫则藏在这里。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, we have located a shrink ray in a secret lab, and once we take this shrink ray, we will have the capability to pull off the true crime of the century.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们查到一间秘密实验室里藏着缩小射线，只要我们把它到手，我们就能够犯下真正意义上的世纪大案

yingyinNormal.en: Well, the holographic principle suggests that what we all experience every day in three dimensions may really just be information on a surface located at the farthest reaches of our cosmos.
yingyinNormal.zh: 全息原理提出的观点是：人类每天在三维空间感受的一切，可能只是宇宙最遥远的地方的全息投影，我们感受到的宇宙其实是外界的信息。
